{
  "texts": [
    "The development of AI-based medical diagnosis enables personalized and science-based approaches to medical care.",
    "However, ethical considerations must be carefully weighed; strategies must be developed to mitigate patient privacy data security and algorithmic bias and to minimize unintended consequences of AI-based medical diagnosis.",
    "Blockchain technology can address patient privacy and data security in future work by providing decentralized storage and secure access controls for patient data.",
    "With blockchain, the training of the AI models is transparent and auditable, improving algorithmic bias and enabling accountability, which is a cornerstone of trusted AI-based medical diagnosis.",
    "NCCT images of 341 patients containing a distal ureteral stone, phlebolith, or both CNN No 92% 8% Cui et al."
  ]
}